#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The path of the skin relative to the application data path (&eg; "
"<filename>skins/default</filename>)."
msgstr ""
"Sökvägen till skalet i förhållande till programmets datasökväg (t.ex. det "
"förvalda skins/)."

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "nb-countries"
msgstr "nb-countries"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of countries (42 in the default skin). There should be the same "
"number of country groups below."
msgstr ""
"Antal länder (42 i standardskalet). Det ska finnas lika många landsgrupper "
"nedan."

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "nb-nationalities"
msgstr "nb-nationalities"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of nationalities (6 in the default skin). There should be the "
"same number of nationality groups below."
msgstr ""
"Antal nationaliteter (6 i standardskalet). Det ska finnas lika många "
"nationalitetsgrupper nedan."

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "nb-continents"
msgstr "nb-continents"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of continents (6 in the default skin). There should be the same "
"number of continent groups below."
msgstr ""
"Antal kontinenter (6 i standardskalet). Det ska finnas lika många "
"kontinentgrupper nedan."

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "pool"
msgstr "pool"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The path and name of the pool file relative to the skin path (&eg; "
"<filename>Images/pool.svg</filename>)."
msgstr ""
"Sökväg och namn på pool-filen i förhållande till skalets sökväg (t.ex. "
